name: Kings of the Electric Wisps
description: Hailing, shockingly, from within the storms that rumble over the plains of Kharth, the Kings of the Electric Wisps are known for their exceptional candescent flashmarble craftsmanship. Now finished uncovering the origin of the Clouddrop wisps, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
